    <p>Mailing lists are the primary communication channels for the FreeBSD
      community, and cover many topic areas.</p>

    <h2>Mailing list archives</h2>

    <p>You can
      <a href="&base;/search/search.html#mailinglists">search</a>
      or <a href="https://www.FreeBSD.org/mail/">browse</a>
      the mailing list archives at
      <a href="https://www.FreeBSD.org/">www.FreeBSD.org.</a>
      It is also possible to
      <a href="https://lists.FreeBSD.org/mailman/listinfo">browse</a>
      the mailing lists via the Mailman Web interface.</p>

    <h2>English Mailing lists</h2>

    <p>The English speaking mailing lists are <a
      href="&base;/doc/en_US.ISO8859-1/books/handbook/eresources-mail.html">listed
      in the FreeBSD Handbook</a>.</p>

